headline: Dodge & Cox Global Bond Fund Q4 2024 Shareholder Letter
summary: Stronger-than-expected U.S. economic data as well as the U.S. election outcome contributed to higher long-term yields globally and a stronger U.S. dollar. Read more here.

headline: Dodge & Cox Income Fund Q4 2024 Shareholder Letter
summary: U.S. Treasury yields surged in the fourth quarter, driven by stronger-than-expected U.S. economic activity and concerns regarding the outlook for the federal deficit and inflation.

headline: Dodge & Cox Balanced Fund Q4 2024 Shareholder Letter
summary: The S&P 500 Index rose by 26.3% in 2023 and posted a 25.0% return in 2024, marking its largest consecutive annual gains since 1998. Read more here.
